snippet.title: PAKU PAKU - PlayStation 4 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Do you like Pac-Man? Can you handle this version of the game?

Pac-man in 1 dimension, can you collect all the coins and escape from the ghost?

Your goal is to collect as many coins as possible without getting caught by the ghost. The score will multiply each time you collect all the coins. You can eat a special coin that will allow you to eat the ghost and earn extra points.

PAKU PAKU (C) Xitilon
